summary: A lore-friendly farmhouse located centrally to five northern cities.  This house mod is built with Frostfall in mind and geared toward players using that mod.
descriptionHtml:
A lore-friendly farmhouse located centrally to Winterhold, Dawnstar, Windhelm, Morthal, and Whiterun -- roughly in the center of the five cities.  This house mod is built with Frostfall in mind as I am in the middle of a Frostfall run myself.

Contents:

1 alchemy table
1 enchanting table
1 bookcase (the lame kind)
1 cooking pot
4 weapon plaques (2 horizontal, 2 vertical bow plaques)
1 blacksmith forge
1 tanning rack
1 sharpening wheel
1 armor table
1 double bed
3 single beds
various chests, barrels, and containers

Location:  See map in images

Known issues:  couldn\'t get the stupid carrots on the cupboard to sit right.  Food on dinner table may jostle easily.
author: Larinon
